{"prompt": "Generate a website for a local artist portfolio. The website should be bold and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Artist Portfolio</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #0a2342;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #0a2342;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid #2ca58d;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #000000;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            color: #a7d2cb;\n        }\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #2ca58d;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid #ffffff;\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .gallery-item {\n            background-color: #123a5e;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .gallery-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n        }\n        .gallery-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 250px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n        }\n        .gallery-item h3 {\n            margin: 15px 0 5px 0;\n            color: #2ca58d;\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n        }\n        .gallery-item p {\n            margin: 0 15px 15px 15px;\n            color: #a7d2cb;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #0a2342;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            border-top: 5px solid #2ca58d;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #a7d2cb;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Artistic Visions</h1>\n            <p>Bold creations by a local artist</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"gallery\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>My Work</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/123a5e/2ca58d?text=Abstract+Blue\" alt=\"Abstract Artwork 1\">\n                    <h3>Oceanic Dreams</h3>\n                    <p>An exploration of deep blues and turbulent textures.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/123a5e/2ca58d?text=Bold+Lines\" alt=\"Abstract Artwork 2\">\n                    <h3>Geometric Force</h3>\n                    <p>Sharp lines and strong forms in striking shades.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/123a5e/2ca58d?text=Abstract+Sky\" alt=\"Abstract Artwork 3\">\n                    <h3>Azure Horizon</h3>\n                    <p>Capturing the vastness of the sky in a bold palette.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/123a5e/2ca58d?text=Textured+Art\" alt=\"Abstract Artwork 4\">\n                    <h3>Urban Pulse</h3>\n                    <p>Reflecting the city's energy with vibrant blues.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Me</h2>\n            <p style=\"width: 70%; margin: 0 auto;\">I am a passionate artist specializing in bold abstract compositions. My work often features intense blues, exploring themes of nature, emotion, and urban landscapes. Each piece is crafted to evoke a strong visual impact and a lasting impression.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Artist Portfolio. All rights reserved. | Contact: <a href=\"mailto:artist@example.com\">artist@example.com</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}